'''Great Rehabilitation Centre National Narcotic Board Indonesia''' ([[Balai Besar Rehabilitasi Badan Narkotika Nasional Indonesia]], Babesrehab) is located in [[Bogor]], [[Indonesia]]. This rehabilitation centre was inaugurated by [[Tien Soeharto]], on 31 October 1974.<ref name="Ulfah">{{id}} Ulfah, Maria. “Metode Therapeutic Community Bagi Residen Narkotika di Unit Terapi dan Rehabilitasi Badan Narkotika Nasional, Lido-Bogor.” Skripsi S.Sos.I, Universitas Islam Negeri, 2011.</ref> This rehabilitation centre service addict using [[one stop centre]] system, which is composed by medical rehabilitation services and social rehabilitation under one roof.<ref name="OSC">{{id}} Pusat Terapi & Rehabiltasi Badan Narkotika Nasional Indonesia. Modul Pelatihan Petugas Rehabilitasi Sosial Dalam Pelaksanaan Program One Stop Centre (OSC), 2006.</ref> This rehabilitation centre service using the [[Therapeutic Community]] (TC) with a capacity of 500 persons, and lasted for 6 months.<ref name="WP">{{id}} Pusat Terapi & Rehabilitasi Badan Narkotika Nasional Indonesia. Walking Paper: Konsep Therapeutic Community, 2009.</ref>

